          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Albanian monetary unit (1/100 of a lek).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">QINDAR — 15 pts</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Variant spelling of qintar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">QAT — 12 pts</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">A plant whose leaves are chewed as a stimulant.</p>
