      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Category 3: Power Tile Combos (25 Words)</h2>
      <p>These short words use Z (10), X (8), J (8), and K (5) tiles to score big from just 3-5 letters. When you draw power tiles, you want to deploy them fast for maximum impact rather than holding them and clogging your rack.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ZAX</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">19 pts</span></span>
